         <p>Related material: School of Forestry and Environmental Studies, Yale University, Student records for the Classes of 1902-1991 (RU 261), Manuscripts and Archives, Yale University Library.</p>  
      </relatedmaterial>
      <scopecontent id="aspace_3ebfcb16aa3d5c3ef6f41a173edc4f8a">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The records consist of grade cards (transcripts) maintained by the Yale School of Forestry (called the School of Forestry and Environmental Studies after 1972).</p>  
      </scopecontent>
